        {
            "title": "港股早市中段升幅逐漸收窄 兩萬七得復失暫升不足300點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股今早一度重越兩萬七關口，但恒生指數衝上27143點、升534點後暫欠再升動力，於上午約10時半過後重新回吐至27000點之下。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">截至上午約11時04分，恒生指數升幅收窄至293點或1.1%，報26902點；恒生科技指數升0.71%，恒生金融分類指數則升1.17%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴(09988)升幅收窄至約3.4%，滙控(00005)與友邦(01299)升幅亦縮至不足2%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15577971-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e6%97%a9%e5%b8%82%e4%b8%ad%e6%ae%b5%e5%8d%87%e5%b9%85%e9%80%90%e6%bc%b8%e6%94%b6%e7%aa%84-%e5%85%a9%e8%90%ac%e4%b8%83%e5%be%97%e5%be%a9%e5%a4%b1%e6%9a%ab%e5%8d%87%e4%b8%8d%e8%b6%b33",
